Okay, so I've been digging into the `damon_stat` code and it looks like there are some serious issues lurking in there. The main concern revolves around how the context is handled when enabling and disabling the statistical data collection, particularly with the `damon_stat_start` and `damon_stat_stop` functions, as well as concurrency issues during module initialization.

